{"title":"Infecciones Espinales-2024-1","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Infectología/Infecciones Espinales-2024-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Infecciones\\NEspinales","guid":"1NgilUr97r8p5FfP-jC1QA","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Infecciones\\NEspinales","guid":"rVETXI7Qlgr4DD6k_vVRqQ","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"1. Definición:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"• Infecciones espinales incluyen:","guid":"EAp2J0StqgZvCl2Lbagb-w","children":[{"id":"4","parent":"3","text":"• Osteomielitis","guid":"rTcIuxciqdeT1XdA9QOpJw","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"3","text":"• Disquitis","guid":"a6akRzVR5ZgkoFGhDaphEg","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"3","text":"• Absceso epidural espinal.","guid":"HKRhlgx89eto3EtJXmSMQQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"2","text":"• Causa: Bacterias, principalmente Staphylococcus aureus\\N→ vía quirúrgica, diseminación hematógena o contigua.","guid":"WZgeEtODgmKYnp7JYVy2HQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"1","text":"2. Factores\\Nde Riesgo:","guid":"3VLYQxM69kag55gS4WqBDQ","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"• Inmunosupresión","guid":"dIN2gPuQuwoI8RJ7yaLgrQ","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"• Bacteriemia","guid":"ADNCDsCu2Jmg9Odrmw7PPw","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"9","text":"• Cirugía reciente.","guid":"DIn0WXs7AP0qupvMC9Ky6A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"12","parent":"1","text":"3. Presentación\\NClínica:","guid":"BgfyN2IMGQx3HBQGcsnkcg","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"• Síntomas inespecíficos:","guid":"7iDLXhcGybO4Eyn0x3SpFQ","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"• Dolor lumbar","guid":"38NZIjMQL3a0z-JZeA356g","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"13","text":"• Fiebre.","guid":"VmgDHCvsdHmHr7V5r9sIDw","children":[]}]},{"id":"16","parent":"12","text":"• Depende de la localización/extensión:","guid":"KJpsvj2wMs5-hxSLE0N_vA","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"• Signos de compresión medular.","guid":"NtKWjFgPECggcP729LN9HA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"18","parent":"1","text":"4. Diagnóstico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"• Dificultad → síntomas inespecíficos y solapamiento con infecciones subyacentes.","guid":"JmWp3AkCWaR7td9XWpMVmA","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"18","text":"• Pruebas:","guid":"xxDpW7CsotJIX9la6JjNPw","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"• Hemocultivos","guid":"DuLEvJrwHo5Pk4TOXwNxtg","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"20","text":"• Marcadores inflamatorios","guid":"Ism89DPJNf4zj14keq3hmg","children":[]}]},{"id":"23","parent":"18","text":"• Imagen avanzada\\Nde la columna:","guid":"cPpW1lSjv-Slv_Ni80xoMw","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"• 1ª línea: RM con y sin contraste.","guid":"KuXVHBhY0aQ5nKywzguBeQ","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"23","text":"• Biopsia guiada por TC si RM negativa.","guid":"QsCKwRKaOeo1eCM1qcPjRw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"1","text":"5. Manejo:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"• Inestabilidad hemodinámica/compromiso neurológico:","guid":"eu1FSJOi9D9XkTVceMUP_w","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"• ATB inmediato → derivación urgente a neurocirugía.","guid":"sYxA-lFfE6D0lMpqpDIw6Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"26","text":"• Pacientes estables:","guid":"7Qf0DSrQa8I-NnXG6eMXgA","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"• Esperar identificación del organismo causante antes de iniciar ATB.","guid":"ptSoNlrYl7riqJ2mvRd_vQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"26","text":"• Manejo quirúrgico adicional:","guid":"BIOuqsozN_ZjFBj4oCIgBA","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"• Abscesos, deformidad espinal, dolor severo persistente, o falla al tratamiento ATB.","guid":"9MSZ2Ruv27nxvUqp8SMCtQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"0","text":"Infecciones Espinales:\\NDefinición y Subtipos","guid":"swJaqaBddvCg9f1HAWCVhg","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"1. Osteomielitis vertebral (espondilitis):\\NInfección del cuerpo vertebral.","guid":"","children":[{"id":"35","parent":"34","text":"• Subtipos:","guid":"3Znm-hmBUHjBeGt73eSJ1g","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"• Osteomielitis vertebral\\Ngranulomatosa:","guid":"O07z8eOxAxDC9FKoALdvDg","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"• Causa: Tuberculosis (enf. de Pott).","guid":"Lo-558lG-16FeeYWKooMbw","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"36","text":"• Factores de riesgo: Inmigración de países con alta prevalencia de TB, coinfección con VIH.","guid":"K_K1dP7nGZ_0OZvaVwLBhA","children":[]}]},{"id":"39","parent":"35","text":"• Osteomielitis\\Nvertebral piógena:","guid":"RmioEUhI7F2aVQuXFu2W0g","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"• Forma más común.","guid":"uCWarhBXgACJuvwIfw_i0g","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"39","text":"• Causa: Infección secundaria por Staphylococcus aureus.","guid":"QydCZjjvfGCFMBms6HPmiA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"42","parent":"33","text":"2. Disquitis: Infección del espacio intervertebral.","guid":"GcR7Duiku4btbAJHLGeyOw","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"33","text":"3. Espondilodiscitis: Infección del cuerpo vertebral y del espacio intervertebral.","guid":"6PdMeZpjyzvhHyiIx_FqXw","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"33","text":"4. Absceso epidural espinal: Infección supurativa en el espacio epidural.","guid":"m9RQpPwldJX7pvBrSromiw","children":[]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"0","text":"Infecciones Espinales:\\NEpidemiología y Etiología","guid":"At_5KKaPYUuvQ8LFj3Jwtg","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"1. Epidemiología:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"• Incidencia: ∼ 5. 4/100,000 (2013) (3).","guid":"RJen4CWdBcB8elneETKSyw","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"• Sexo: ♂ > ♀ (2).","guid":"-b49RW9zFpfrLA8rsGIK_g","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"46","text":"• Edad promedio: 59-69 años (2).","guid":"1O-HEHUPRemR9sj0UxroNw","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"46","text":"• Datos epidemiológicos: Referidos a EE. UU. salvo que se indique lo contrario.","guid":"YU2EYRgmKJvkzaacU_BWIg","children":[]}]},{"id":"51","parent":"45","text":"2. Etiología:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"• Vías de\\Ninfección:","guid":"_t86ix2vATCeJrUJkpptPg","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"• Diseminación hematógena: Desde un foco distante (e.g., infección de piel y tejidos blandos, ITU).","guid":"K0cXj_6n1mqOCtnLJQMt-Q","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"52","text":"• Inoculación directa: Durante cirugía espinal o por trauma.","guid":"tqpcwuEvOsSw2kZwG_2HAQ","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"52","text":"• Diseminación contigua: Desde infecciones adyacentes (e.g., aorta, esófago).","guid":"wyyCjRmhsRhmuXzqv3cvyg","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"52","text":"• Sin fuente primaria identificable: Frecuente.","guid":"xdaSQWLjX56bikpY63O2-w","children":[]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"51","text":"• Patógenos\\Ncomunes:","guid":"YIZfPXQwEu4Xz4UkxYNXiQ","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"• Staphylococcus aureus (>40% de los casos) (2).","guid":"K52js4t_QisEGZT6PLgELA","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"57","text":"• Escherichia coli (2° más común).","guid":"m_PXGbRHuFek2HSOeaPRrg","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"57","text":"• Pseudomonas aeruginosa.","guid":"eD0V8bcwNpP6i1OSN6LCNw","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"57","text":"• Proteus mirabilis.","guid":"cOuu_kkjCQ6ptAUujKy3_Q","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"57","text":"• Enterobacteriaceae.","guid":"Gg3O_kx1qDnv0hjB89mTkQ","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"57","text":"• Estreptococos beta-hemolíticos.","guid":"rxO4p_hYrAMsvxex9WhPLw","children":[]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"51","text":"• Pacientes\\Nespeciales:","guid":"D4cVRMNCIWBhioXCCDKUNA","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"• Post cirugía espinal: Staphylococcus epidermidis, Propionibacterium acnes.","guid":"cJbidrSHgxAmfGWFtXJkLg","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"64","text":"• Endemicidad alta/emigración: Mycobacterium tuberculosis (espondilitis tuberculosa), Brucella spp.","guid":"i_-iAheYxb7z-36EcwbVkg","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"64","text":"• Inmunocompromiso/catéteres venosos/drogas IV: Considerar hongos.","guid":"tF563Uw6rZWRPDePy1UmRA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"68","parent":"45","text":"3. Factores\\Nde Riesgo:","guid":"9eIzwr2HruqVDmlLW0mpwQ","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"• Edad > 50 años (5).","guid":"-saqMyRTZLZot-Q3T6le2g","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"68","text":"• Anemia falciforme (8).","guid":"h75_HfvN57caNjSKSxvsdQ","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"68","text":"• Inmunocompromiso (uso de esteroides, VIH).","guid":"NkfzZOTmAG0WSeon7xxwfw","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"68","text":"• Uso de drogas IV.","guid":"q-L0ZWGEuZEffyXG2zWChA","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"68","text":"• Bacteriemia reciente.","guid":"Gsk10wRRg7V0B1TH2MHifw","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"68","text":"• Endocarditis infecciosa.","guid":"aiJtXWV0e0lQc5ILdgtNbA","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"68","text":"• Cirugía espinal reciente e instrumentación.","guid":"K11nyD3jX_TasHQTySG8ew","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"68","text":"• Dispositivos intravasculares.","guid":"H4W1kTnVY6_ucezh4UV4sA","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"68","text":"• Malnutrición.","guid":"1JQEOEYfBUs-ceeHLvmYeA","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"68","text":"• Condiciones\\Nmédicas crónicas:","guid":"qwCBxa0AjN2VYYz-O8ukAQ","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"• DM","guid":"dGwn2CnWAo0M5T_2JCSSYQ","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"78","text":"• Falla renal","guid":"K7zZVUyOVx88DQeADtsv-g","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"78","text":"• Enfermedad cardíaca","guid":"nfiuMfa8eVUwQ-Iwa3rMdw","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"78","text":"• Cirrosis hepática.","guid":"52O9zKoetW1S2Ch0u-Rvrg","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"78","text":"• Malignidad.","guid":"4pKDCfeV3Hx_4pWVHAMB6g","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"0","text":"Características\\NClínicas:","guid":"DAJHkzj9eHEJEE3miF-N0A","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"• Dolor lumbar\\No cervical:","guid":"ukqq1ATSW7uMTou2LxVEjg","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"• Inicio insidioso → empeora semanas/meses.","guid":"2kvuro_me5uHP9E9og_1GA","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"85","text":"• Localizado.","guid":"tX1Iad6yCIm9Dje-v00-8A","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"85","text":"• Peor con actividad física y durante la noche.","guid":"FS2tCzG5oxVFWOBrhRnKZg","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"85","text":"• Puede irradiarse a abdomen, cadera, pierna, escroto, ingle, periné.","guid":"Dptpwt3NoiQfofpXMef7hA","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"85","text":"• Dolor agudo y severo → sospechar absceso epidural.","guid":"1T7-OuBjJ1V02xipwXm8ag","children":[]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"84","text":"• Examen físico:","guid":"qCgspgDLdsyKy_94bHvbNQ","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"• Dolor exacerbado por palpación/percusión del área afectada.","guid":"fUHsHzlBZxvDspdzXWBc0Q","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"91","text":"• Palpación de músculos paravertebrales → sensibilidad y espasmo.","guid":"tBi9HY8noswindNvtLYHdw","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"91","text":"• Movilidad espinal reducida.","guid":"LBHvwrIKQe7vyfbvf2bYTw","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"91","text":"• Signos/síntomas neurológicos","guid":"nm27tszVBJf9cEZMAB4A_Q","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"91","text":"• Fiebre: presente en hasta 45% de los pacientes (6).","guid":"nwfW7-CBEmdFUcQ9dMz_Ww","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"97","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico:","guid":"tszMMrDbmMUnl2JhnWfo8Q","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"• Enfoque:","guid":"-mpNBH2fJGA_KdIOXyr_lA","children":[{"id":"99","parent":"98","text":"• Pruebas iniciales en todos los\\Npacientes sospechosos:","guid":"iApQ4Yt9eFFcKyCPViRjDQ","children":[{"id":"100","parent":"99","text":"• VSG y PCR.","guid":"uY0AetFvGILxRefPg2l0iQ","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"99","text":"• Dos hemocultivos (aerobios y anaerobios).","guid":"5Ny4HcuNz2HKC5Nm3zGwWg","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"99","text":"• RM columna.","guid":"V91_0USuw1CCqmrPJ1tVCA","children":[]}]},{"id":"103","parent":"98","text":"• Si las pruebas iniciales son negativas pero la\\Nsospecha clínica es alta, considerar:","guid":"K419BZooSFyDaCpXqb3MAQ","children":[{"id":"104","parent":"103","text":"• Gammagrafía nuclear.","guid":"BBFeyQ9XO-WpV1KovMsxag","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"103","text":"• Biopsia por aspiración guiada por TC.","guid":"W1nVCL_XIKO5YTVAGdRY2A","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"103","text":"• Sospecha de diseminación hematógena o contigua\\N→ identificar/tratar la causa subyacente.","guid":"hd9TcOnWKhcjDd1dMYqmDg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"107","parent":"97","text":"• Estudios de\\Nlaboratorio:","guid":"jpm0T5otIpl-basxUjSAcA","children":[{"id":"108","parent":"107","text":"• ↑ PCR, ↑ VSG (6).","guid":"C6w5YqLJS804QZ5eupl1BA","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"107","text":"• Hemograma: típicamente elevado (6).","guid":"y22mLHUUFryKt1NlCHtxjg","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"107","text":"• Hemocultivos: dos series, aerobios y anaerobios,\\Nde dos sitios de punción venosa.","guid":"ybZJv1xx99EMBW47AeRiMw","children":[]}]},{"id":"111","parent":"97","text":"• Pruebas adicionales si se sospechan\\Npatógenos menos comunes:","guid":"5eDaXsGuxrses5w4ybuQAQ","children":[{"id":"112","parent":"111","text":"• Brucella: Hemocultivos y serología.","guid":"UOHL0YEYhfyIxQu_vwtNUA","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"111","text":"• Infecciones fúngicas: cultivos de hongos, serología, detección de antígenos.","guid":"5mzv1QReQPYntITUPih7bA","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"111","text":"• Tuberculosis: PPD, prueba de liberación de IFN-γ, o cultivo micobacteriano.","guid":"G5LyktIEgk3RxVXX1DbsVQ","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"111","text":"• Si no hay signos de infección en las pruebas iniciales, considerar\\Nelectroforesis de proteínas séricas para evaluar mieloma múltiple.","guid":"rlZcXiXzUrq_JTaYEx6W8A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"116","parent":"0","text":"• Estudios\\Nde imagen:","guid":"iHGGaz7-v2FPcf12OT3GVA","children":[{"id":"117","parent":"116","text":"• RM columna: 1ª línea para sospecha de\\Ninfección espinal (mayor sensibilidad) (6).","guid":"byUaO1wLKpXq-tDomiMRgA","children":[{"id":"118","parent":"117","text":"• Modalidad: RM con y sin contraste IV de gadolinio.","guid":"5VYfz6B_HUsdxrMjATDwNA","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"117","text":"• Hallazgos:","guid":"hJCPsNJOSS51lzyznX_RLA","children":[{"id":"120","parent":"119","text":"• Osteomielitis\\Nvertebral piógena:","guid":"C9imrdas4j_Jk4TB2rJ_xA","children":[{"id":"121","parent":"120","text":"• Pérdida de definición de placas vertebrales + cambio en señal de discos y cuerpos vertebrales\\N(hipointenso en T1, hiperintenso en T2).","guid":"CnK14lDTonSj0DlgZfounw","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"120","text":"• Realce de contraste en discos y cuerpos vertebrales.","guid":"-260ld7gHvRAnq5thUYKNw","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"120","text":"• Inflamación de tejidos blandos adyacentes.","guid":"oECEuy0E58nup5WaG8OKxg","children":[]}]},{"id":"124","parent":"119","text":"• Absceso\\Nepidural espinal:","guid":"0QYHnKpIWIuOKVJJxvp6xA","children":[{"id":"125","parent":"124","text":"• Infección temprana (flemón): realce homogéneo en espacio epidural.","guid":"_MZZ8oIfFEfi90buIWdymA","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"124","text":"• Absceso establecido: realce en anillo rodeando un centro no realzado.","guid":"AYRfoJEJNEbIOWhHrpX3Dw","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"127","parent":"116","text":"• TC columna con\\Ncontraste IV:","guid":"MoxZLICIkguAuky8wE1FYA","children":[{"id":"128","parent":"127","text":"• Indicaciones:","guid":"BErkINiov7KVySZKRdoibg","children":[{"id":"129","parent":"128","text":"• Evaluación de calcificaciones o secuestros.","guid":"TInlwx4VYxwIkcFGaz6lwg","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"128","text":"• Biopsia por aguja percutánea.","guid":"jtWKKXTOw7nVN3og-dd0Ig","children":[]}]},{"id":"131","parent":"127","text":"• Hallazgos:","guid":"xnegWEV_eYk3nTDUwU5jbg","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"• Edema óseo adyacente.","guid":"dyZnJz4TiXphP5QpBUMqTg","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"131","text":"• Estrechamiento del espacio intervertebral.","guid":"s2jV-eEsglwBev93EgbaWg","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"131","text":"• Erosión de placas vertebrales.","guid":"t9RAuB_zIbLooyl9G3eGAw","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"131","text":"• Formación de secuestros.","guid":"RlHkqRkPNlh0rRKEzdFqqw","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"131","text":"• Calcificaciones.","guid":"EWicowq1DCfRhOxEYjlA2A","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"131","text":"• Absceso epidural espinal: realce en anillo tras administración de contraste.","guid":"wjw_QS2cRiCEiBsxhwawEg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"138","parent":"116","text":"• Gammagrafías nucleares: complemento a la RM si\\Nresultados iniciales son negativos o equívocos:","guid":"oE-n6pT-l0I5RDu4saWLLw","children":[{"id":"139","parent":"138","text":"• Modalidades: combinación de escaneos.","guid":"Lxyz3ZkW2Nf3K6Pe36pp5w","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"138","text":"• Gammagrafía ósea con tecnecio-99m en 3 fases.","guid":"SVnmHJsl7Gmc5dlcCbRL7w","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"138","text":"• Escáner de galio.","guid":"UQmnlZyqsLjopHcVYVv5_g","children":[]}]},{"id":"142","parent":"116","text":"• PET scan.","guid":"Grb4pt5WkzsKYAGH9UEnQg","children":[{"id":"143","parent":"142","text":"• Hallazgos: aumento de actividad en el área infectada.","guid":"IREBCf-zrjufV3tERiYSLQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"144","parent":"116","text":"• Radiografía:","guid":"gHQF5X76K_Ir2lzVFRYGDA","children":[{"id":"145","parent":"144","text":"• Indicaciones: no se usa para diagnóstico de infecciones espinales,\\Npero posible estudio inicial en paciente con dolor lumbar.","guid":"QDeU3zz85RGo5auoxFyicA","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"144","text":"• Hallazgos:","guid":"e-VNLdUqOSWOJM7pBXF9ZQ","children":[{"id":"147","parent":"146","text":"• Normal durante las primeras 3-6 semanas de infección (6).","guid":"2pVzVWxn5IKFqDZTfBKgyA","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"146","text":"• Después de\\N3-6 semanas:","guid":"J1GsjhyAlJ52bQACI5IT8A","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"• Estrechamiento del espacio intervertebral.","guid":"gGOysKue-ijSPKIugAf2Mg","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"148","text":"• Erosión de placas vertebrales.","guid":"mq5Gh30rtmRr_0q6yZHTRw","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"148","text":"• Engrosamiento periostal.","guid":"sdLAKqxVEH7TtkfZ9-ge-g","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"148","text":"• Lesiones líticas.","guid":"aOIxQSIT0GKSs8htigwPVA","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"148","text":"• Aparición de nuevo hueso.","guid":"5n-N_cUMNZ99Y3FIYqPK3g","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"148","text":"• Cambios en tejidos blandos paravertebrales.","guid":"IbaIa8xvu74zyBsV4Ir1-Q","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"155","parent":"116","text":"• Biopsia por aspiración\\Nguiada por TC:","guid":"-bEeN-qEoMBHe0eZdEtzlA","children":[{"id":"156","parent":"155","text":"• Prueba confirmatoria.","guid":"S5Y60wpzVsSffYVh-cuPTA","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"155","text":"• Biopsia del área afectada → análisis microbiológico y patológico.","guid":"QChPff58GpWEpCwwAJt4Wg","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"155","text":"• Indicaciones para\\Nrepetir la biopsia:","guid":"HgljSviw5LzYdvn9JuXs7g","children":[{"id":"159","parent":"158","text":"• Tejido insuficiente.","guid":"Ge-R8ZhNCE5_EHuzfyxAEg","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"158","text":"• Muestra contaminante de piel probable.","guid":"hs0K6YrQ3JVEfUSZrJHQFg","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"158","text":"• Organismo sospechoso de difícil cultivo\\N(e.g., hongos, micobacterias, Brucella spp).","guid":"ZixpzMHs8ABjwF7ba8FrzA","children":[]}]},{"id":"162","parent":"155","text":"• Indicaciones:","guid":"RDYU4CxY52P74Nqum-ZWqA","children":[{"id":"163","parent":"162","text":"• Pacientes con infección espinal sin identificación de\\Norganismo causante en hemocultivos o serología.","guid":"D4zj--rFTEVOm9o7XKUPWg","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"162","text":"• Considerar en pacientes con osteomielitis vertebral\\Nsospechada y bacteriemia concurrente.","guid":"xAJcGBM84Ln91U3m-l81Iw","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"162","text":"• En pacientes con trabajo diagnóstico no concluyente y biopsia negativa, pero alta sospecha\\Nclínica de infección espinal, realizar una nueva biopsia (guiada por TC o quirúrgica) (6).","guid":"Vri1TlTS4_hSqLdATMb7bg","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"166","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento:","guid":"HcDZ8KdzNxCgrCqVZTjccA","children":[{"id":"167","parent":"166","text":"• Enfoque\\Ninicial:","guid":"Z_FX9EaKzX0sbY3JcIW28g","children":[{"id":"168","parent":"167","text":"• Evaluar necesidad de ATB empírico y tratamiento invasivo.","guid":"fZvrTWc2f1vkrCHa4m1_KA","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"167","text":"• Iniciar ATB empírico y obtener cultivos +\\Nconsulta neurocirúrgica urgente si:","guid":"3Fk-LIPWgx5t-ciYbN82kw","children":[{"id":"170","parent":"169","text":"• Sospecha de absceso epidural espinal.","guid":"eJ5jTIzaetTwJCc87nwoLA","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"169","text":"• Nuevos o progresivos síntomas neurológicos.","guid":"9JgzJU4FWmuxYCydva4yTw","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"169","text":"• Inestabilidad hemodinámica o sepsis inminente.","guid":"FpHC2j1wqGwQGRhIOEV_SQ","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"169","text":"• Si no se cumplen estos criterios, retrasar ATB\\Nhasta identificación del organismo causante.","guid":"rHU3QjjIhFes9zQgmWGduw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"174","parent":"166","text":"• Continuación:","guid":"CSbKGDbSv32NxrvjJdAt1g","children":[{"id":"175","parent":"174","text":"• Iniciar manejo del dolor.","guid":"f8g48AGjRyZn1qaaKiY7Ig","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"174","text":"• Si la movilidad es limitada, comenzar medidas preventivas contra úlceras por decúbito.","guid":"Ai8RYQvQKSfhhj-gMFD56w","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"174","text":"• Identificar y tratar causas subyacentes.","guid":"sTmaB5u4CirtVfDX7P5nnw","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"174","text":"• Revaluar regularmente en busca de nuevos signos/síntomas neurológicos.","guid":"PPNlRy6xMFjh-okj_aey9Q","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"174","text":"• Adaptar ATB basado en cultivos y resultados de susceptibilidad.","guid":"cyk6QWYJzR6q338HXS5ibQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"180","parent":"0","text":"Terapia\\NAntimicrobiana:","guid":"2vsHA89_JkIyJl4YxDXkOw","children":[{"id":"181","parent":"180","text":"• Terapia\\Nempírica:","guid":"e5hktymK-1xYv4OfkZRMcg","children":[{"id":"182","parent":"181","text":"• Indicaciones: Nuevos síntomas neurológicos, inestabilidad hemodinámica, sepsis.","guid":"1xAOsi8F2OT9oqWL82gvDQ","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"181","text":"• Cobertura: Staphylococcus spp., incluyendo MRSA, Streptococcus spp. y bacilos gramnegativos.","guid":"nHwwjyf3EhK8q-OLK0CsDg","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"181","text":"• Regímenes\\Nrecomendados:","guid":"DxbZul6SYkUKuOoSykisGw","children":[{"id":"185","parent":"184","text":"• 1ª línea: Vancomicina + cefalosporina de 3ª generación (e.g., ceftriaxona)\\No cefalosporina de 4ª generación (e.g., cefepima).","guid":"VASYYYEjYROCg1dk6lDfAw","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"184","text":"• Alternativa si alergia: Daptomicina + fluoroquinolona (e.g., ciprofloxacino).","guid":"aGpP-JdsZ56USe2spXCiuQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"187","parent":"180","text":"• Terapia antimicrobiana\\Nespecífica:","guid":"Ze3SmrnwjlY4wQss33EcHw","children":[{"id":"188","parent":"187","text":"• Iniciar tratamiento IV basado en cultivos y susceptibilidad.","guid":"4tLN89Akh9qP6GJZZB182Q","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"187","text":"• Considerar cambio a ATB oral si síntomas mejoran y\\Nmarcadores inflamatorios disminuyen.","guid":"LXBheMdOeQznOy7dt9KaTQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"190","parent":"180","text":"Terapia antibiótica específica\\Npara osteomielitis vertebral:","guid":"0E_z_OEjFJtuOyclKgvmGA","children":[{"id":"191","parent":"190","text":"• Staphylococcus\\N(MSSA):","guid":"Mg9m2GXJy25BPWk-PnntTw","children":[{"id":"192","parent":"191","text":"• Preferido: Nafcilina u oxacilina.","guid":"ps29ZSbOOJgnlSHA2aTYFA","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"191","text":"• Alternativas: Cefazolina, ceftriaxona, vancomicina, daptomicina,\\Nlinezolid, levofloxacino + rifampicina, clindamicina.","guid":"Yy6gWjJFhpYOuaLELTgpew","children":[]}]},{"id":"194","parent":"190","text":"• Staphylococcus\\N(MRSA):","guid":"_Ew9gyHKxepBdQhNEh3oEA","children":[{"id":"195","parent":"194","text":"• Vancomicina, daptomicina, linezolid, levofloxacino + rifampicina.","guid":"zr8ChPGnZLn2EIy845mU9A","children":[]}]},{"id":"196","parent":"190","text":"• Enterococcus\\N(sensible a penicilina):","guid":"VFxp6QQhHcJjM4uDCyeAcw","children":[{"id":"197","parent":"196","text":"• Penicilina G, ampicilina,\\Nvancomicina, daptomicina, linezolid.","guid":"8gYJa5NeIuhEntl4LE_Glg","children":[]}]},{"id":"198","parent":"190","text":"• Enterococcus\\N(resistente a penicilina):","guid":"kFq-q1rDj-333lQE23i2Rw","children":[{"id":"199","parent":"198","text":"• Vancomicina, daptomicina, linezolid.","guid":"FnZSXBnuuwiXT_UiGN_8IA","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"198","text":"• Pacientes también deben recibir un aminoglucósido (e.g., gentamicina).","guid":"XCoNDuCsZPbSFuiODfTS8A","children":[]}]},{"id":"201","parent":"190","text":"• Pseudomonas\\Naeruginosa:","guid":"V-GikV6wDhxTXcqcUQLs3w","children":[{"id":"202","parent":"201","text":"• Cefepima, meropenem, doripenem,\\Nciprofloxacino, ceftazidima, aztreonam.","guid":"yHsmlTZoEzaTOPQ7GysV8A","children":[]}]},{"id":"203","parent":"190","text":"• Enterobacteriaceae:","guid":"fLUWsGqHYfWepqo5eoNY7g","children":[{"id":"204","parent":"203","text":"• Cefepima, ertapenem, ciprofloxacino.","guid":"DQT5Lmd-uUv4wqB2U5DxGw","children":[]}]},{"id":"205","parent":"190","text":"• Streptococcus beta-hemolítico:","guid":"xPQUB0cB-dr5KECL8-pmdA","children":[{"id":"206","parent":"205","text":"• Penicilina G, ceftriaxona, vancomicina.","guid":"rLFQfgZE3Ax_BFXV2Yyz5A","children":[]}]},{"id":"207","parent":"190","text":"• Propionibacterium acnes:","guid":"P-N0zguD4RO87Q-hZrOIqA","children":[{"id":"208","parent":"207","text":"• Penicilina G, ceftriaxona, clindamicina, vancomicina.","guid":"yVtgi8xuaYRA_u96O7rhXA","children":[]}]},{"id":"209","parent":"190","text":"• Salmonella spp.:","guid":"ypu31g3CYzo85oEWk0XD0Q","children":[{"id":"210","parent":"209","text":"• Ciprofloxacino, ceftriaxona.","guid":"06kpQudcVEUFx49qnLZUqg","children":[]}]},{"id":"211","parent":"190","text":"• Mycobacterium tuberculosis:","guid":"JzNLH6oQ6s7LQBXkEMG64Q","children":[{"id":"212","parent":"211","text":"• Ver “Tratamiento de tuberculosis.”","guid":"mBdjYnS2-PbVLUzRs7VI1A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"213","parent":"180","text":"Duración del\\Ntratamiento:","guid":"dFK4_sFVJ10XyxdnBplbTA","children":[{"id":"214","parent":"213","text":"• Generalmente, 6 semanas de ATB, pero puede variar según el organismo causante y respuesta del\\Npaciente. Consultar a un especialista en enfermedades infecciosas antes de finalizar el tratamiento.","guid":"Hsn93Lb1Yfu6IkENLjsnbA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"215","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento\\NInvasivo:","guid":"r6JD5fwM7FdJ2ffdcZ3W0A","children":[{"id":"216","parent":"215","text":"• Drenaje e irrigación\\Nguiados por TC:","guid":"JGP85BJ8kxFm_bwvRDJVnA","children":[{"id":"217","parent":"216","text":"• Indicaciones: Abscesos epidurales y paravertebrales.","guid":"3mTLweW_wulhuVohBwaYbw","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"216","text":"• Contraindicaciones: Absceso anterior, inestabilidad espinal, osteomielitis o espondilodiscitis asociada.","guid":"DKtsdLpXS3MBb-71Eoaq4A","children":[]}]},{"id":"219","parent":"215","text":"• Cirugía:","guid":"WK357rAfLTY4HGSQaz-4VQ","children":[{"id":"220","parent":"219","text":"• Indicaciones:","guid":"-P3gnv_euFmSvd1ySwSW_w","children":[{"id":"221","parent":"220","text":"• Abscesos epidurales y paravertebrales grandes (≥ 2.5 cm).","guid":"Q90bCTOwKwmWJ_0EE7oMmQ","children":[]},{"id":"222","parent":"220","text":"• Inestabilidad o deformidad espinal.","guid":"eYz8q03w7vw0ja8S-HqL3g","children":[]},{"id":"223","parent":"220","text":"• Deterioro neurológico nuevo o progresivo.","guid":"3832W1D1qAyzvfrML1x_pQ","children":[]},{"id":"224","parent":"220","text":"• Dolor intratable.","guid":"n8ixmp_71UW-SPesC5Xegg","children":[]},{"id":"225","parent":"220","text":"• Necesidad de biopsia abierta.","guid":"zhkGuVBWPn6nIy4vetO3jg","children":[]},{"id":"226","parent":"220","text":"• Infecciones asociadas con implantes espinales.","guid":"qIFsKbxdNabnVZT7QOqeoQ","children":[]},{"id":"227","parent":"220","text":"• Infección persistente o recurrente en el torrente sanguíneo.","guid":"vn_YYhxXzDTBDV_IqLfs8w","children":[]}]},{"id":"228","parent":"219","text":"• Objetivos:","guid":"x4rNiFZUuWip0w1yo69mDQ","children":[{"id":"229","parent":"228","text":"• Desbridamiento de tejidos infectados y, si es necesario, remoción de material protésico.","guid":"YRkczjFkong49hjq1hEw7A","children":[]},{"id":"230","parent":"228","text":"• Obtención de material para evaluación microbiológica/histológica.","guid":"ZIFGbai7-RsrD12muaTeaw","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"228","text":"• Descompresión de estructuras neurales.","guid":"h9OiG0jMtY_SZRHel4Xu8Q","children":[]},{"id":"232","parent":"228","text":"• Fijación espinal.","guid":"ozYuUjnZ7QjSIVMjqYaURg","children":[]},{"id":"233","parent":"228","text":"• Drenaje de abscesos.","guid":"ZqTor3a7gEbuOVZZ-1CpkQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"234","parent":"0","text":"Complicaciones:","guid":"NpbCgO_LM0NRNEhZpbmMcw","children":[{"id":"235","parent":"234","text":"• Neurológicas:","guid":"aw2ytJ498Sswy0-it38t9g","children":[{"id":"236","parent":"235","text":"• Debilidad motora o parálisis.","guid":"nFKosB9AnCkqMPApNYpnGA","children":[]},{"id":"237","parent":"235","text":"• Pérdida sensorial.","guid":"_rzl1SUb20smwXgsqlkvnw","children":[]},{"id":"238","parent":"235","text":"• Meningitis.","guid":"hIOtWPrYQ5BurN-MqVBYpg","children":[]}]},{"id":"239","parent":"234","text":"• Infecciosas:","guid":"WdFz-9nDLhXgrYe80CF-3A","children":[{"id":"240","parent":"239","text":"• Sepsis.","guid":"M74LFyf_F_5AjpsPLsL1ZA","children":[]}]},{"id":"241","parent":"234","text":"• Abscesos en tejidos\\Nblandos circundantes:","guid":"6girJvOfOuOkmei8ZralAg","children":[{"id":"242","parent":"241","text":"• Absceso prevertebral: Puede manifestarse con dolor cervical, disfagia, dificultad respiratoria,\\Ny potencial fallo respiratorio (por compresión traqueal y obstrucción de la vía aérea).","guid":"stLzG4BixFfQh5YBaMq54w","children":[]},{"id":"243","parent":"241","text":"• Absceso paravertebral: Síntomas frecuentemente se solapan con los de la infección espinal subyacente.","guid":"gS2Vw9xl30HPQYe_-RLlCw","children":[]},{"id":"244","parent":"241","text":"• Absceso del psoas.","guid":"QhwtF4trbdYmNCP-8bBjiA","children":[]},{"id":"245","parent":"241","text":"• Aortitis infecciosa.","guid":"5Q-9o9jbNUeBotmsAOBfYQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"246","parent":"0","text":"Recomendaciones\\NIDSA 2015","guid":"5ozSFhmkd0_D9w9F7N28mQ","children":[{"id":"247","parent":"246","text":"Recomendaciones Diagnósticas para\\NOsteomielitis Vertebral Nativa (NVO)","guid":"5eT4cu0OLspn85qe0w6Y5A","children":[{"id":"248","parent":"247","text":"I. Cuándo Considerar el\\NDiagnóstico de NVO","guid":"8Qtl9_6Ng_WUQlKAdyp7rg","children":[{"id":"249","parent":"248","text":"1. Dolor de espalda/cuello (nuevo/empeoramiento) + fiebre","guid":"07FJN3hKh3iDkCBVl8ZPaQ","children":[]},{"id":"250","parent":"248","text":"2. Dolor de espalda/cuello (nuevo/empeoramiento) + ↑VSG o PCR","guid":"IG-gkGLPw91giAUGZFRnKw","children":[]},{"id":"251","parent":"248","text":"3. Dolor de espalda/cuello (nuevo/empeoramiento) + bacteriemia o endocarditis infecciosa","guid":"3Ol1DO4vxUVXvxwkaJ3g3A","children":[]},{"id":"252","parent":"248","text":"4. Fiebre + síntomas neurológicos nuevos ± dolor de espalda","guid":"Fh8EOioSmH41uYityvYudQ","children":[]},{"id":"253","parent":"248","text":"5. Dolor localizado de cuello/espalda (nuevo) + infección reciente por S. aureus","guid":"5EDNo7ynA70LOIl91abufQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"254","parent":"246","text":"Evaluación Diagnóstica Apropiada en\\NPacientes con Sospecha de NVO","guid":"VM_ZnaC2bhI6EcP5jY7wSg","children":[{"id":"255","parent":"254","text":"II. Evaluación\\NDiagnóstica","guid":"a-CYqx-VBHybsciuYQA02Q","children":[{"id":"256","parent":"255","text":"6. Examen médico + neurológico (motor/sensitivo):","guid":"9XE-_RDouyGEFb88CKvqgw","children":[{"id":"257","parent":"256","text":"• Realizar en todos los pacientes con sospecha de NVO (fuerte, bajo).","guid":"aTcxnAWBeNBNXbhVMaKWow","children":[]}]},{"id":"258","parent":"255","text":"7. Cultivos sanguíneos (aerobios y anaerobios, 2 sets) + VSG/PCR basal:","guid":"72udNc0UwSBmkp56eCDa0Q","children":[{"id":"259","parent":"258","text":"• Realizar en todos los pacientes con sospecha de NVO (fuerte, bajo).","guid":"B7Aw7S-4MbiErB746yqENg","children":[]}]},{"id":"260","parent":"255","text":"8. RM columna:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"261","parent":"260","text":"• Realizar en pacientes con sospecha de NVO (fuerte, bajo).","guid":"q-UQMvXcu3cLb3hk7kfctQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"262","parent":"255","text":"9. Alternativa a RM (si no disponible o contraindicado):","guid":"iCBEFqFnUBXpP5T2BbHegw","children":[{"id":"263","parent":"262","text":"• Gammagrafía gallio/Tc99 + scan óseo, TC o PET scan (débil, bajo).","guid":"q1ZYu1BRWsF5xiVjgGff8Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"264","parent":"255","text":"10. Cultivos sanguíneos + serología para Brucella:","guid":"OLK9g3z8HE_TnePFTHvZAQ","children":[{"id":"265","parent":"264","text":"• Realizar en pacientes con NVO subaguda en áreas endémicas de brucelosis (fuerte, bajo).","guid":"dFC8S7jgRLF3dMH-umbhXw","children":[]}]},{"id":"266","parent":"255","text":"11. Cultivos sanguíneos para hongos:","guid":"vyZX6_E5sMp0fRSEurzwRw","children":[{"id":"267","parent":"266","text":"• Considerar en pacientes con sospecha de NVO y riesgo de infección fúngica (débil, bajo).","guid":"i6JFn8cOVTtIVkIIS3W7Jw","children":[]}]},{"id":"268","parent":"255","text":"12. PPD o interferón-γ:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"269","parent":"268","text":"• Considerar en pacientes con NVO subaguda y riesgo de Mycobacterium tuberculosis (débil, bajo).","guid":"aSqeC5LVRMmixXa20A_d4g","children":[]}]},{"id":"270","parent":"255","text":"13. Evaluación por especialista en enfermedades infecciosas y cirujano de columna:","guid":"qCQqpK0z7qjjadIsKufObg","children":[{"id":"271","parent":"270","text":"• Considerar en pacientes con sospecha de NVO (débil, bajo).","guid":"SJb9OXfnjP3afAqCAzqVsQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"272","parent":"246","text":"Aspiración-Biopsia Guiada por Imagen y\\NEstudios Adicionales en NVO","guid":"pO1eE9N7ZspwQd5NewSzkQ","children":[{"id":"273","parent":"272","text":"III. Indicaciones para\\NAspiración-Biopsia Guiada por\\NImagen o Estudios Adicionales","guid":"9QxxdsdeaAmi_IFv3h7n8w","children":[{"id":"274","parent":"273","text":"14. Aspiración-biopsia\\Nguiada por imagen:","guid":"7iR2LIb2uJcQGoMssrNC_A","children":[{"id":"275","parent":"274","text":"• Recomendada en pacientes con sospecha de NVO (basado en clínica, laboratorios e imágenes) cuando no se ha establecido un dx\\Nmicrobiológico para organismos conocidos (S. aureus, S. lugdunensis, Brucella spp.) mediante hemocultivos o serologías (fuerte, bajo).","guid":"yH7Jhp_QVZYNRuNLGi3-Fg","children":[]}]},{"id":"276","parent":"273","text":"15. Contraindicación de\\Naspiración-biopsia guiada por imagen:","guid":"5WW1BuEg5EeGZwwB0ZEzBw","children":[{"id":"277","parent":"276","text":"• No realizar en pacientes con infección sanguínea por S. aureus, S. lugdunensis o Brucella spp.\\Ncon sospecha de NVO según clínica, laboratorios e imágenes (fuerte, bajo).","guid":"s7F9OL_n09CO1Lo8naxsdg","children":[]}]},{"id":"278","parent":"273","text":"16. Contraindicación de\\Naspiración-biopsia guiada por imagen:","guid":"S1uRsbNvX8_cDNVlQJSGrQ","children":[{"id":"279","parent":"278","text":"• No realizar en pacientes con sospecha de NVO subaguda (en áreas endémicas) y\\Nserología fuertemente positiva para Brucella (fuerte, bajo).","guid":"iBh7pDzksrrLL4YJ4xKBEA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"280","parent":"246","text":"Duración del Retiro de Terapia Antimicrobiana\\Nantes de Aspiración-Biopsia en NVO","guid":"dIL5opvWBxRlAL64OMjk2w","children":[{"id":"281","parent":"280","text":"IV. Duración de la Retirada de ATB antes de\\NAspiración-Biopsia Guiada por Imagen","guid":"0Ws8WTadHRd8AIKsKDY9lw","children":[{"id":"282","parent":"281","text":"17. Intervención\\Ninmediata:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"283","parent":"282","text":"• En pacientes con compromiso neurológico ± sepsis inminente o inestabilidad hemodinámica, se\\Nrecomienda intervención quirúrgica inmediata + inicio de terapia antimicrobiana empírica (fuerte, bajo).","guid":"KroCrkDUjfq7yJWiJpLwIQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"284","parent":"246","text":"Cultivos Fúngicos, Micobacterianos o de\\NBrucella Tras Aspiración-Biopsia Guiada\\Npor Imagen en NVO","guid":"RXVogdNq0yzQoiSsvmWwAg","children":[{"id":"285","parent":"284","text":"V. Indicaciones para Cultivos\\NEspecializados después de\\NAspiración-Biopsia","guid":"C35-CCj9MQ4xwUlzhaO7rg","children":[{"id":"286","parent":"285","text":"18. Cultivos fúngicos,\\Nmicobacterianos o de Brucella:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"287","parent":"286","text":"• Sugeridos en muestras de biopsia/aspiración guiadas por imagen en pacientes con sospecha de NVO si existen\\Nfactores de riesgo epidemiológicos, del huésped o pistas radiológicas características (débil, bajo).","guid":"TDad6G5KklY9ULWk5njb7Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"288","parent":"285","text":"19. Cultivos fúngicos, micobacterianos y pruebas de\\Namplificación de ácidos nucleicos bacterianos:","guid":"hIZf9HRy6EdTyLG0eSmSfg","children":[{"id":"289","parent":"288","text":"• Sugeridos en muestras almacenadas apropiadamente si los cultivos bacterianos\\Naeróbicos/anaeróbicos no muestran crecimiento en pacientes con sospecha de NVO (débil, bajo).","guid":"W4DL1jlFR21df850Xh3HvQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"290","parent":"246","text":"Envío de Muestras para Examen Patológico Tras\\NAspiración-Biopsia Guiada por Imagen en NVO","guid":"J6qQ4kbvzymZhFqQdtLF1Q","children":[{"id":"291","parent":"290","text":"VI. Indicaciones para Enviar\\NMuestras a Examen Patológico","guid":"LBpX2geKG6Euy5gmVJ3Hug","children":[{"id":"292","parent":"291","text":"20. Envío de muestras para\\Nexamen patológico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"293","parent":"292","text":"• Si se puede obtener tejido adecuado de manera segura, se debe enviar muestras patológicas de todos los pacientes para confirmar\\Nel diagnóstico de NVO y guiar pruebas diagnósticas adicionales, especialmente en el contexto de cultivos negativos (fuerte, bajo).","guid":"a_qCAl_AVWluYb_SsL7S_A","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"294","parent":"246","text":"Pasos a Seguir en Pacientes con\\NBiopsia-Aspiración Guiada por Imagen No\\NDiagnóstica y Sospecha de NVO","guid":"Jf7g4mGey1tQ06BxOdQA_Q","children":[{"id":"295","parent":"294","text":"VII. Pasos Siguientes en Casos de\\NBiopsia-Aspiración No Diagnóstica","guid":"fxjqQdNGHTFosQyZcYPSiw","children":[{"id":"296","parent":"295","text":"21. Segunda\\Naspiración-biopsia:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"297","parent":"296","text":"• Recomendada si no hay infección sanguínea concomitante y la primera muestra de biopsia aspirativa guiada por imagen creció un\\Ncontaminante cutáneo (estafilococos coagulasa-negativos [excepto S. lugdunensis], Propionibacterium spp., o difteroides) (fuerte, bajo).","guid":"Hdipwlg_5iUdIoUvuy-HEw","children":[]}]},{"id":"298","parent":"295","text":"22. Pruebas adicionales:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"299","parent":"298","text":"• Realizar en pacientes con primera biopsia aspirativa no diagnóstica y sospecha de NVO para excluir organismos de difícil cultivo\\N(anaerobios, hongos, Brucella spp., o micobacterias) (fuerte, bajo).","guid":"ISXrSCvT2PDGZCJZq0E_7Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"300","parent":"295","text":"23. Opciones tras biopsia y\\Nestudios no diagnósticos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"301","parent":"300","text":"• Repetir biopsia aspirativa guiada por imagen, realizar discectomía endoscópica\\Npercutánea y drenaje (PEDD) o proceder con biopsia excisional abierta (débil, bajo).","guid":"jXbTq9ujx936UjltWUxo5A","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"302","parent":"246","text":"Terapia Clínica en NVO: Inicio de\\NTratamiento Antimicrobiano Empírico","guid":"Xalhcte6BkIDG2QG1yZZHQ","children":[{"id":"303","parent":"302","text":"VIII. Cuándo Iniciar Terapia\\NAntimicrobiana Empírica en NVO","guid":"-QNPpEnp0HjYqxv7sb9SAg","children":[{"id":"304","parent":"303","text":"24. Retraso de\\Nterapia empírica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"305","parent":"304","text":"• En pacientes con examen neurológico normal y estable + hemodinámicamente estables, se sugiere\\Nposponer la terapia antimicrobiana empírica hasta establecer un diagnóstico microbiológico (débil, bajo).","guid":"LiVa72Rvqyo6yi5k1wHlkA","children":[]}]},{"id":"306","parent":"303","text":"25. Inicio de\\Nterapia empírica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"307","parent":"306","text":"• En pacientes con inestabilidad hemodinámica, sepsis, shock séptico, o síntomas neurológicos graves/progresivos, se sugiere\\Niniciar terapia antimicrobiana empírica junto con un intento de establecer un diagnóstico microbiológico (débil, bajo).","guid":"vy2gGsnYW0cnq6kD5cu_Uw","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"308","parent":"246","text":"Duración Óptima de la Terapia\\NAntimicrobiana en NVO","guid":"255W6yAtsYUlNZOUfEzvSA","children":[{"id":"309","parent":"308","text":"IX. Duración de la\\NTerapia Antimicrobiana","guid":"R3UO_5UiDE6TizlmNtdIDQ","children":[{"id":"310","parent":"309","text":"26. Duración total\\Nde 6 semanas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"311","parent":"310","text":"• Recomendada para la mayoría de los pacientes con NVO bacteriana. Puede ser terapia\\Nparenteral o vía oral con antimicrobianos altamente biodisponibles (fuerte, bajo).","guid":"wsb3_a3eIeql606f6TKvAQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"312","parent":"309","text":"27. Duración total\\Nde 3 meses:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"313","parent":"312","text":"• Recomendada para la mayoría de los pacientes con\\NNVO por Brucella spp. (fuerte, moderado).","guid":"tEidj4ENgera_PkmAnYy_A","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"314","parent":"246","text":"Indicaciones para\\NIntervención Quirúrgica en\\NNVO","guid":"_Mv4Z4PiUOsF9zZDWa5-xQ","children":[{"id":"315","parent":"314","text":"X. Indicaciones para Intervención\\NQuirúrgica en Pacientes con NVO","guid":"_6464JxK5a3k-DmJwUkBgg","children":[{"id":"316","parent":"315","text":"28. Intervención\\Nquirúrgica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"317","parent":"316","text":"• Recomendada en pacientes con déficits neurológicos progresivos, deformidad progresiva e\\Ninestabilidad espinal con o sin dolor a pesar de terapia antimicrobiana adecuada (fuerte, bajo).","guid":"N8XTWaNfHIhYmG0DqtsGYw","children":[]}]},{"id":"318","parent":"315","text":"29. Desbridamiento\\Nquirúrgico ± estabilización:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"319","parent":"318","text":"• Sugerido en pacientes con infección sanguínea persistente o recurrente (sin fuente\\Nalternativa) o dolor que empeora a pesar de terapia médica adecuada (débil, bajo).","guid":"m4Xe2tAjQs4PR0wf1AYWwA","children":[]}]},{"id":"320","parent":"315","text":"30. Contraindicación de desbridamiento\\Nquirúrgico y/o estabilización:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"321","parent":"320","text":"• Desaconsejado en pacientes con empeoramiento de las imágenes óseas a las 4-6 semanas en el\\Ncontexto de mejoría en los síntomas clínicos, examen físico y marcadores inflamatorios (débil, bajo).","guid":"oWoQaeBlLqXZW85gqAwr3w","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"322","parent":"246","text":"Seguimiento Clínico en NVO:\\NDefinición de Fracaso Terapéutico","guid":"O00WsL7l0Hy009T3goYDxw","children":[{"id":"323","parent":"322","text":"XI. Definición de Fracaso de la Terapia en\\NPacientes con NVO Tratados","guid":"YVZH3u2J1yZnVjBJAkeqGg","children":[{"id":"324","parent":"323","text":"31. Criterios para no\\Nconsiderar fracaso terapéutico:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"325","parent":"324","text":"• Dolor persistente, déficits neurológicos residuales, marcadores inflamatorios sistémicos elevados, o hallazgos radiográficos\\Npor sí solos no necesariamente indican fracaso del tratamiento en pacientes con NVO tratados (débil, bajo).","guid":"8NFxkX0Fvms6-SgLU-9eOg","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"326","parent":"246","text":"Seguimiento de NVO: Marcadores\\NInflamatorios Sistémicos y RM","guid":"mm7c4_mnTfjOuH3gXnwJig","children":[{"id":"327","parent":"326","text":"XII. Rol de Marcadores Inflamatorios\\NSistémicos y RM en el Seguimiento de\\NPacientes Tratados con NVO","guid":"7J0elNQQqBHXuft6c7y7Vg","children":[{"id":"328","parent":"327","text":"32. Monitorización de marcadores\\Ninflamatorios sistémicos (VSG y/o PCR):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"329","parent":"328","text":"• Sugerida después de aproximadamente 4 semanas de terapia\\Nantimicrobiana, en conjunto con evaluación clínica (débil, bajo).","guid":"56RwwVZgaqMahfb7K2C3dw","children":[]}]},{"id":"330","parent":"327","text":"33. RM de seguimiento:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"331","parent":"330","text":"• No recomendada de manera rutinaria en pacientes con NVO que muestran una\\Nrespuesta clínica y de laboratorio favorable a la terapia antimicrobiana (fuerte, bajo).","guid":"rGLdmgJ_UbnJK6qZCTLFkA","children":[]}]},{"id":"332","parent":"327","text":"34. RM de seguimiento en\\Nrespuesta clínica pobre:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"333","parent":"332","text":"• Sugerida para evaluar cambios evolutivos en tejidos blandos epidurales y paraspinales en\\Npacientes con NVO que presentan una respuesta clínica pobre a la terapia (débil, bajo).","guid":"WBSOlX6-0PERvhHR1TvABw","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"334","parent":"246","text":"Enfoque en Pacientes con NVO y\\NSospecha de Fracaso Terapéutico","guid":"OrxytDruXC7XHjEMeC3eeA","children":[{"id":"335","parent":"334","text":"XIII. Manejo de Pacientes con NVO y\\NSospecha de Fracaso Terapéutico","guid":"5aIspz-sWpO3wkUc8nVVDQ","children":[{"id":"336","parent":"335","text":"35. Marcadores de inflamación\\Nsistémica (VSG y PCR):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"337","parent":"336","text":"• Sugerido obtener en pacientes con NVO y sospecha de fracaso terapéutico. Valores sin cambios o en aumento\\Ndespués de 4 semanas de tratamiento deben aumentar la sospecha de fracaso terapéutico (débil, bajo).","guid":"ZwZBpCqpynCxzPZLIadvkA","children":[]}]},{"id":"338","parent":"335","text":"36. RM de seguimiento:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"339","parent":"338","text":"• Recomendada para evaluar cambios evolutivos en tejidos blandos paraspinales y\\Nepidurales en pacientes con NVO y sospecha de fracaso terapéutico (fuerte, bajo).","guid":"O4fB_1z9NhFHGu9n652h_w","children":[]}]},{"id":"340","parent":"335","text":"37. Obtención de\\Nmuestras adicionales:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"341","parent":"340","text":"• Sugerido en pacientes con evidencia clínica y radiográfica de fracaso terapéutico. Realizar exámenes microbiológicos (bacterias,\\Nhongos, micobacterias) y anatomopatológicos mediante biopsia aspirativa guiada por imagen o muestras quirúrgicas (débil, muy bajo).","guid":"96uN63i-wLRMyPcAL3PKiw","children":[]}]},{"id":"342","parent":"335","text":"38. Consulta con cirujano de columna y\\Nespecialista en enfermedades infecciosas:","guid":"WydN6dgyRwamgTPdi8vnBg","children":[{"id":"343","parent":"342","text":"• Sugerida en pacientes con NVO y evidencia clínica y\\Nradiográfica de fracaso terapéutico (débil, muy bajo).","guid":"08pi0b6xBxwBIeZqmoiITA","children":[]}]}]}]}]}]},"node_count":343,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Infectología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Infectología","filename":"Infecciones Espinales-2024-1","id":"map_1143","resolved_references":[]}